hey jme, ashford is pretty close to me!, well your cousins house is the closest thing to me it appears. I remember this frappr from ages ago.

That reminds me, I decided not to go there anymore so I will remove myself from there, lol.

[/quote]

ah ok, it pretty much sucks where i live
